John Morris (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Morris_(actor) 0 John Charles Morris (born October 2, 1984) is an American voice actor. He is best known for his role as the voice of Andy Davis in the Toy Story film trilogy. John_Charles_Morris ( born October_2_,_1984 ) is an_American_voice_actor .
